viewData.name: Natural Look Eyelashes 40
viewData.short_description: The PhiNesse eyelashes are natural and handmade. Each eyelash is made to look as natural as possible.
viewData.long_description: The PhiNesse eyelashes are natural and handmade. Each eyelash is made to look as natural as possible. The eyelashes are soft, flexible, easy to apply and comfortable to wear.  The Natural Look eyelashes are designed to achieve a very realistic and natural look and are also suitable for daily use. They are super light, comfortable and feel natural during the day.
